folder: East River Drive & 26th Street (East), Manhattan, NY
text:
East River Drive, at the foot of East 26th Street, showing details where the former New York Yacht Club basin was. A concrete fill will extend the land several hundred feet, providing a new roadway and wharfage facilities. The latter will be used by the New York Yacht Club. The one story structure shown is their former boat house.

October 13, 1939
No's. 1-2-3

P. L. Sperr
